snippet.title: Man Eater Truth Quest DLC Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2021
snippet.description: Conspiracy theories and bull sharks are a match made in heaven in Maneater's latest DLC, Truth Quest. Check out this trailer ahead of the launch of Maneater: Truth Quest on PC, PlayStation and Xbox on August 31.
